Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:33.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! I can't believe this! - OG}I don't believe it!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:36.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Oniwabanshu... - OG}The Oniwabanshu captains...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:38.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and the Mimawari-gumi... - OG}and the Mimawari-gumi's, too...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:40.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Most of them are beaten! - OG}{they're almost all down! - Polly}Most of them are down!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:42.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Daikoku{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:43.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Kazekage-sama! - OG}Lord Kazekage!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:45.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Captain Hotei!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.34,0:01:52.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is what the legendary\Nyakuza is capable of?! - OG}So that's what the legendary\Nyakuza is capable of, huh?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:56.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He resisted turning into an ice ogre\Nbut took advantage of its power! - OG}He resisted the effects of the ice ogre,\Nbut still took advantage of its power!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.10,0:01:59.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I now understand a little why Wano... - OG}I think I'm beginning to understand...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:03.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{has been so feared... - OG}why Wano has been so feared...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:17.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boss Hyogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:22.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for, Yatappe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Empty your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:31.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If I turn into an ice ogre...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.14,0:02:38.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:40.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Just give me a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:42.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna do it soon! - OG}I'm gonna do it!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna do it now! - OG}I'll do it right now!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Of course it's hard... - OG}Of course it's difficult...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:50.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's like... - OG}After all, that man...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{a father to us! - OG}is like a father to us!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tsunagoro, cut me without hesitation! - OG}Tsunagoro, cut me down right now!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:04.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boss Hyogoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I'll join you soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Omasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:14.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! - OG}Dammit!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:18.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can't you make it\Nin time somehow?! Tanuki-san! - OG}{Isn't there any way you can\Nmake it in time, Mr. Tanuki?! - Polly}Isn't there any way you can\Nfinish in time, Mr. Tanuki?!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I can't endure it anymore, either! - OG}I can't fight it anymore, either!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I have no chance to survive! - OG}There's no saving me now!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.27,0:03:25.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't make me... - OG}Don't let me...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boss Omasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:36.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't make me hurt you all! - OG}Don't let me hurt you all!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.11,0:03:37.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Mr. Tanuki{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:39.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Isn't the cure ready yet?! - OG}Surely the cure is ready by now?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.20,0:03:42.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This whole floor... - OG}The entire floor...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:44.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and our friends... - OG}all of our companions...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{will be taken over by ice ogre again! - OG}{will be overtaken by the ice ogre once more! - Polly}will succumb to the ice ogre once more!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.13,0:03:53.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Queen-sama! - OG}Your Awesomeness!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:56.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Queen-sama! - OG}Your Awesomeness!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:04:02.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're your subordinates... Why do\Nwe have to die from your virus?! - OG}We work for you, man... Why do we\Nhave to die from your virus, too?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:11.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up, you peons! - OG}Shut your mouths, you lowlifes!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.36,0:04:16.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You fools are useless now! - OG}You punks have outlived your usefulness!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.03,0:04:18.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Listen! - OG}{Listen good! - Polly}Listen up!{Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:22.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{If I have no use for you, you're garbage! - OG}If I can't use you, you're as good as trash!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.46,0:04:32.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ice ogre is my masterpiece virus! - OG}{Ice ogre is my crowning achievement! - Polly}The ice ogre virus is my\Ncrowning achievement!{Polly+Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:36.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{In fact, it's meant for you guys. - OG}{If anything, it was practically made for you! - Polly}If anything, it was made especially for you!{Polly+Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:38.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, Pleasures!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:43.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've already lost the ability lottery... - OG}You guys already lost the ability lottery!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:47.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're just cannon fodder who can only laugh! - OG}{All cannon fodder like you\Ncan do is sit there and laugh! - Polly}{Now you're just laughing cannon fodder! - Z}Now you're nothing but\Ncackling cannon fodder!{Z+Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:48.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{H-How could you say that?! - OG}{Wh-What do you mean?! - Polly}Th-That's awful!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:52.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, Waiters!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:56.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No matter how long you wait,\Nno more smile fruits are coming! - OG}You can wait all you like, but there're\Nno more smile fruits coming!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:05:00.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys lost your chance to gain powers! - OG}{You guys lost your chance at powers! - Polly}You guys lost your chance to be somebody!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:03.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The forever Waiters. - OG}{You'll be waiting forever! - Polly}The Eternal Waiters.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.24,0:05:06.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As the name suggests, all you can do is wait! - OG}{I guess that's why they call you Waiters! - Polly}It's a fitting name, since all you can do is wait!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:12.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The only way you good-for-nothings\Ncan help the formidable Beast Pirates... - OG}The only way you layabouts can\Nbe of use to the mighty Beast Pirates...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{is to become an ogre before you die, - OG}{is by becoming an ogre before you die, - Polly}is by at least becoming\Nan ogre before you die.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:18.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and do something worthwhile\Nto close out your lives! - OG}{and do something worth a damn\Nwith your final moments! - Polly}That way you can do something\Nworth a damn with your final moments!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:22.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! That's like... you're telling us to die... - OG}So are you saying... we should just die?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes, I am! - OG}Oh! {\i1}Now{\i0} you get it!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:29.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have tons of troops. - OG}We already have plenty of troops.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:32.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How could you say that?! - OG}What an awful thing to say!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's terrible... - OG}{That's horrible... - Polly}No way...{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I gave you a chance! - OG}{I gave you morons a chance! - Polly}You had your chance!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:39.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That antibody could save some of you! - OG}Those antibodies could still save some of you!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:47.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! I'm not gonna die! - OG}Dammit! I'm not gonna die without a fight!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:51.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Slice up your fellow soldiers who turned\Ninto ice ogres! And the samurai! - OG}{Cut down all the ice ogres, samurai or not! - Polly}Cut down every ice ogre,\Nsamurai and allies alike!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go get them! - OG}Now that's what I'm talkin' about!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:05:58.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Fight your asses off to survive!{OG}{Show some survival instincts! - Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.34,0:06:02.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Their master-servant relationship\Nmakes me sick... - OG}{His treatment of\Nhis people is sickening! - Polly}His treatment of his men is sickening!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.59,0:06:04.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, it's so disgusting. - OG}{It truly is disgusting. - Polly}Indeed it is.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, you damn samurai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:11.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You may think you're protecting\Nsomething over there, - OG}{I don't know what it is you think\Nyou're fighting for over there, - Polly}{I don't know who it is you think\Nyou're protecting over there, - Polly}Maybe you don't realize\Nwho you're protecting over there,{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:14.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but don't forget that the tanuki is... - OG}but in case you forgot, that tanuki...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{also a pirate! - OG}{is a pirate, just like us! - Polly}is a pirate, just like us!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.11,0:06:19.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Queen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:23.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Producing many antibodies\Nin just a short amount of time? - OG}{Synthesizing that many antibodies\Nin this short an amount of time?! - Polly}Synthesizing that many antibodies\Nin such a short amount of time?!{Polly+Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:26.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's impossible! - OG}Don't make me laugh!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.91,0:06:32.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure he just administered\Nthe antibody to himself and escaped! - OG}He probably just gave himself\Nthe cure and bailed!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:36.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's different from you guys! - OG}{He's nothing like you blackguards! - Polly}He's nothing like you villains!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How can you be so sure?! - OG}Are you sure about that?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:42.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Pirates do cheat! - OG}{Pirates aren't known for being honest! - Polly}Pirates aren't known for being loyal!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:48.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boss Hyogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:51.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll follow you sooner or later! - OG}I'll be right behind you!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't be so hasty to follow me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.19,0:07:04.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Big Boss!\N– Big Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:11.12,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{Goodbye... - OG}Farewell...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:22.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't stop me, tanuki-san! - OG}Don't try and stop me, Mr. Tanuki!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:38.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We have no choice! - OG}We have no other choice!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:39.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I need you to wait! - OG}Just wait!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:41.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll save him now! - OG}{I'm going to save him! - Polly}I'll save him right now!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boss! Swallow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:52.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes! I made it in time! - OG}Thank goodness! We made it just in time!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,B-Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alright! It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:04.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{His body's gonna warm up! - OG}Your body is warming up!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Boss Hyogoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:24.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:32.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Tanuki-san, I knew you could do it! - OG}I knew you could do it, Mr. Tanuki!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:39.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Miyagi, Tristan! Hurry up! - OG}{Miyagi, Tristan! Quickly! - Polly}Miyagi! Tristan! On the double!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Okay, Dr. Chopper! - OG}Right away, Dr. Chopper!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is that... - OG}What's that?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's all set, Dr. Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:01.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Dr. Chopper! Give us the order! - OG}Dr. Chopper! Just give the order!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– A cannon?!\N– A cannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Chopperphage...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:08.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,192)}Nebulizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shoot! - OG}Fire!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:35.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Inhale the mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:41.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What do you think you're doing, tanuki?! - OG}What do you think you're\Ndoing, you damn tanuki?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:48.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What have you done to my masterpiece?! - OG}{The pinnacle of my work...\NWhat have you done to it!? - Polly}The pinnacle of my work...\NWhat have you done!?{Polly+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:57.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's impossible to give the medicine individually\Nto thousands of warriors on this floor! - OG}{Handing out medicine to thousands of soldiers\Nindividually would be impossible! - Polly}Individually handing out medicine to thousands\Nof soldiers would be impossible!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:02.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So I crafted my own virus out of the antibody! - OG}So I created my own virus\Nusing the antibodies!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:03.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What?! - OG}You what?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:07.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{A bad virus can be beaten by a good virus! - OG}{I can counteract a bad virus with a good virus! - Polly}A good virus can counteract a bad virus!{Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:13.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This way, everyone can ingest\Nthe cure by inhaling the mist! - OG}{By doing it this way, everyone just needs\Nto breathe in the mist to be cured! - Polly}{With this method, everyone just needs\Nto breathe in the mist to be cured! - Polly+Gordy}This way, everyone just needs\Nto breathe in the mist to be cured!{Polly+Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:18.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're just a doctor from\Na petty pirate group's ship... - OG}{You're just some ship doctor\Nfrom a third-rate pirate crew... - Polly}You're just some ship doctor\Nfrom a backwater pirate crew...{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Where did you learn such skills?! - OG}Where did you learn something like this?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We scattered all over the world\Nand trained ourselves! - OG}We scattered all over the world\Nto train for moments like this!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:29.40,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even my subordinates have\Nrecovered from ice ogre! - OG}You even cured my own guys of ice ogre!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:31.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How dare you?! - OG}What gives you the right?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:36.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You shouldn't use a virus\Nin a fight so casually! - OG}{Viruses aren't meant to be\Nused in battle so lightly! - Polly}Who in their right mind\Nwould use a virus as a weapon?!{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It'll surely get out of hand! - OG}{There's no telling when\Nit might get out of hand! - Polly}There's no way to control it!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:48.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why do I have to be taught\Nethics by a tanuki? - OG}I am {\i1}not{\i0} gonna be lectured on\Nethics by a damn tanuki!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who do you think I am?! - OG}Who the hell do you take me for?!{Polly}
Comment: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:00.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pleasures?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:05.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What are you guys doing?! - OG}What the hell are you doing?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:12.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get out of my way, you weaklings! - OG}Stay out of this, you rats!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.69,0:11:14.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Shut up, Queen! - OG}{Shut it, Queen! - Polly}{Give it a rest, Queen! - Z}Up yours, Queen!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:18.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Our brothers were almost killed by you, - OG}{You almost killed our brothers-in-arms... - Polly}You nearly killed our brothers...{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:21.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and were saved by Tanuki-san here! - OG}{but this little tanuki saved our asses! - Polly}but Mr. Tanuki here saved our asses!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:26.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Instead of death due to\Na crazy superior, we'd... - OG}{We'd rather die siding with\Nthe guy who saved us... - Polly}We'd rather die side-by-side\Nwith the guy who saved us...{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:29.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{rather die siding with the one who saved us! - OG}instead of being killed\Nby our crazy-ass boss!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:32.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Isn't that right, guys?! - OG}Ain't that right, boys?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:37.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Thank you, tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:38.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1452,1053)}Tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,1053)}Tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1452,1053)}Tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:45.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,1053)}{I'm indebted to you, Tanuki-san! - OG}We are in your debt,\NMr. Tanuki!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:48.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1452,1053)}{Tanuki-san, thank you! - OG}Mr. Tanuki... Thank you!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:51.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\pos(470,1053)}{I'm so impressed with tanuki. - OG}You're really somethin' else,\Nlittle tanuki.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:12:01.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Tanuki! Tanuki! Tanuki! Tanuki!\N– Tanuki! Tanuki! Tanuki! Tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.86,0:12:01.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}– Tanuki! Tanuki! Tanuki! Tanuki!\N– Tanuki! Tanuki! Tanuki! Tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Go to hell, Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You shitheads! - OG}{You goddamn shitheads! - Polly}You little shits!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:16.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That was impressive, tanuki! - OG}Not bad at all, tanuki!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:21.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Do it! - OG}{Now pop him. - Viz}Now let him have it.{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.68,0:12:23.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's one more thing that I wanna say! - OG}There's just one more thing that I wanna say!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:29.02,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Tanuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:30.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,313)}Rumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Monster Point!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:37.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go! - OG}– Get him!\N– Get him!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.28,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You got this!{Polly}
