Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:56.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There is a big space between\Neach floor of the castle! - OG}There's a bunch of space between\Neach floor of the castle!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No one'll see us there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:12:59.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:03.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Momonosuke-sama! Just a little more patience! - OG}Lord Momonosuke! Please hold on\Njust a little longer!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:06.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke{-kun}, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:09.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I am not okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What are you saying?! - OG}What do you mean?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.86,0:13:20.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I am not okay, I feel bad. - OG}I am not okay. I feel awful.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.53,0:13:22.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.41,0:13:27.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Everyone is overrating me! - OG}{Everyone thinks too highly of me! - Polly}Everyone gives me too much credit!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:38.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I am frivolous, stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:42.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{weak, foolish, and I am sick of myself... - OG}{weak, foolish, and I hate myself... - Polly}weak, foolish, and I make myself sick...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:45.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Momonosuke-sama, you're great! - OG}Lord Momonosuke, I think you're amazing!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.81,0:13:48.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I am not great at all! - OG}I am not amazing at all!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:50.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Even if you're small now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:56.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I know you'll be big and become\Na great shogun one day! - OG}{I know that you'll grow into\Na big and strong shogun one day! - Polly}I know that you'll grow up to\Nbe a proper shogun one day!{Polly+Nikki}
Comment: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I know you'll be big
Comment: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:56.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,and become a great Shogun one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:14:00.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You'll be a greater man\Nthan Kozuki Oden ever was! - OG}You'll be an even greater man\Nthan Kozuki Oden ever was!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:06.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I am not... I am not...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I am not great at all! - OG}I am not amazing at all!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:14.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.54,0:14:15.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,An eel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:17.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Momonosuke-sama! - OG}Lord Momonosuke!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.67,0:14:20.92,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Why do you look like that?{OG}{What happened to you? - Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.55,0:14:27.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is what he becomes when he gets excited. - OG}{This is what happens to him\Nwhen he becomes too emotional. - Polly}This is what happens to Lord Momonosuke\Nwhen his emotions run high.{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:28.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{What? - OG}Huh?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:31.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Could it be because\Nyou ate a devil fruit? - OG}{Is it because you ate\Na devil fruit or something? - Polly}Did you eat a devil fruit or something?{Polly+PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:34.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Yes, I did... - OG}Indeed, I did...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Kaido...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.66,0:14:51.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{when the Marines caught him once... - OG}Back when the Marines\Nhad him held captive...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:58.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{there was a man-made devil fruit\Nwhich Vegapunk created... - OG}Vegapunk extracted Kaido's\Nhereditary elements...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{by extracting Kaido's hereditary elements. - OG}and used them to create\Nan artificial devil fruit.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:05.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The government asked him\Nto hand it over to them, - OG}{Although the government demanded\Nit be turned over to them, - Polly}The government requested\Nthat he hand over the fruit,{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:09.39,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{but since he viewed it\Nas a disappointing failure, - OG}{Vegapunk viewed it as a complete failure. - Polly}{but apparently, Vegapunk\Nconsidered it a disappointing failure. - Z+Polly}{but apparently, since Vegapunk\Nconsidered it a disappointing failure, - Z+Polly}{but because Vegapunk\Nconsidered it a disappointing failure, - Z+Polly}but since Vegapunk\Nconsidered it a disappointing failure,{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:13.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{it was kept at Punk Hazard for a long time. - OG}{As a result, it was kept at\NPunk Hazard from that point onward. - Polly}{As a result, it was stored\Nat Punk Hazard long term. - Polly+Z}it was stored at Punk Hazard long term.{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:17.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Why are you bringing that up now? - OG}Why bring that up now?{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:19.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Punk Hazard was detonated. - OG}{Punk Hazard was destroyed. - Polly}Punk Hazard was blown up.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That should be gone forever.... - OG}{That fruit should be gone now. - Polly}The fruit should be gone now.{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:24.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I hope it was destroyed in the explosion, - OG}I can only hope it was\Ndestroyed in that explosion,{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.32,0:15:30.41,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,but Marine Branch G-5 reported\Nthat one facility was still in operation...{OG}{but according to Marine Branch G-5,\Nthere was still one facility in operation. - Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.66,0:15:39.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm just really glad that it was a failure... - OG}I'm just grateful... that it was a failure.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.81,0:15:53.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who healed us? - OG}Who treated our wounds?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't know... - OG}I do not know...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But I think I saw the person... - OG}{But I thought I did see someone... - Polly}But I believe I may have seen someone...{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:01.11,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, I must've been dreaming... - OG}No, it must have been a dream...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:04.78,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's impossible... - OG}After all, it could not have been...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.61,0:16:12.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy-dono and the others are fighting Kaido for us. - OG}Sir Luffy and his allies are\Nengaging Kaido in our stead.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:15.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We should not be staying\Nhere and doing nothing! - OG}We should not stay here and sit idly by!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:18.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The battle on the island is still on! - OG}{The battle for this island still rages on! - Polly}The battle for this island rages on!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.96,0:16:20.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go! - OG}Let us move!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:23.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We still have life left to give!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Guys! - OG}You guys!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're badly beaten! - OG}You look like hell!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I missed you all! - OG}{I've missed you guys! - Polly}{I've missed you all! - Polly}How I've missed you all!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:41.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You've became quite old! - OG}You're so much older now!{Viz}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:53.74,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{O-Oden-sama! - OG}L-Lord Oden!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:57.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oden-sama? - OG}Lord Oden?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.21,0:17:03.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No wonder you're surprised! - OG}It's no wonder you're surprised!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.84,0:17:06.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I was sent to the future\Nwith Toki's special power! - OG}Toki sent me here to the future\Nwith the help of her ability!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:08.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll explain it to you later. - OG}I'll explain everything later.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:09.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,It's a long story!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oden-sama! - OG}Lord Oden!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That is why you are here! - OG}So that is why you are here!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:18.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry for being late! - OG}{I'm sorry for being so late! - Polly}Sorry for being late!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:22.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But we can't rejoice in our reunion forever! - OG}But we don't have time to catch up right now!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go! - OG}{It is time! - Polly}Now come!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{To face Kaido who we\Nfailed to take down that day! - OG}{We'll finish what we started\Nwith Kaido so long ago! - Polly}{We go to Kaido, to finish\Nwhat we started so long ago! - Polly+LP}We go to Kaido, the man\Nwe failed to kill on that fateful day!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:31.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We'll come with you! - OG}We are with you!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.82,0:17:34.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's been our wish from the beginning! - OG}That has been our wish from the beginning!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:36.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go! - OG}{Let us go now! - Polly}Let us depart!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:43.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I knew you guys would say so! - OG}{I knew you guys would agree! - Polly}I knew you guys would say that!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:46.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wait, you guys! - OG}Hold it, everyone!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:50.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's no way he's alive!{OG}{There is no chance he yet lives! - Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:52.01,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,He must be an impostor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:54.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Ashura?!{OG}{How can you say that, Ashura?! - Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:55.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kin'emon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{This is what Toki-sama said! - OG}Remember Lady Toki's words!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:02.39,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,313,1,\3c&H525252&\4c&H000000&)}Travel to the past is impossible...{Wano 09 - 18:42}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.65,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(1860,0,1,\3c&HD0D4D4&\4c&HD0D4D4&)}but one can leap ahead to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.90,0:18:11.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Travel to the past is impossible"!{Wano 09 - 18:42}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:15.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Toki-sama's ability was sending people to the future! - OG}{Lady Toki had the ability\Nto send people to the future! - Polly}Lady Toki's ability was\Nto send people to the future!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.70,0:18:19.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oden-sama died that day! - OG}Lord Oden died that day!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:24.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That fact wouldn't change even in the future! - OG}That fact would not change,\Neven in the future!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:28.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No one can change the past!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.55,0:18:33.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But maybe he is real! - OG}{But... there must be a chance! - Polly}But... it could be him!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.72,0:18:34.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I know! - OG}{I know how you feel! - Polly}{I know that! - Polly}I get that!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:40.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:47.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Wake up, Kin'emon! - OG}{Open your eyes, Kin'emon! - Polly}Snap out of it, Kin'emon!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:53.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:55.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{He's not even bleeding! - OG}He doesn't even bleed!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No way! - OG}Impossible!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ashura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:05.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I thought you pledged to become my samurai. - OG}I thought you had pledged to be my samurai.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:10.75,Flashbacks-207+,,0,0,0,,{\t(2399,0,1,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Be my samurai!{Wano 35 - 15:12}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.30,0:19:15.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ashura{-san}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.72,0:19:18.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ashura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:29.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Now it's clear that he's an impostor... - OG}Now you can see his true colors...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.57,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We all feel the same... - OG}I know we all feel the same...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:36.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wish he were the real one... - OG}I wish he were real as well...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:39.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But he's an impostor! - OG}But... this is an impostor!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How vicious! - OG}How terrible!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.54,0:19:44.62,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Who's posing as Oden-sama then?! - OG}Who could be posing as Lord Oden?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:45.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not him?! - OG}It's not really him?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:47.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Damn! - OG}Dammit!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:54.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Ashura{-san}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.88,0:19:58.18,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But his behavior... - OG}But... his demeanor...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It looks exactly like Oden! - OG}{He acts exactly like Oden! - Polly}It is exactly like Oden's!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:03.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The one who can mimic him so well must be... - OG}The only one who could\Nmimic him so perfectly...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:04.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{one of us! - OG}{would be one of us! - Polly}is one of us!{Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,So it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:12.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1690)}Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.65,0:20:17.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly! I'm Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Ashura-san, I'm sorry! - OG}Ashura, forgive me!{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:22.45,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{No, it's my fault! - OG}{This is all my fault! - Polly}This is my fault!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:25.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Because I failed to finish Kanjuro off, you... - OG}{If only I hadn't failed to finish\NKanjuro off, you wouldn't... - Polly}If I hadn't failed to finish off Kanjuro...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:31.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Even a sharp sword will become dull\Nwhen you try to cut your friend... - OG}{Even a sharp sword will become dull\Nwhen it tries to cut down a friend... - Polly}{Even the sharpest sword will become dull\Nwhen it tries to cut down a friend... - Polly+Goldy}Even the sharpest blade dulls\Nwhen turned on a friend...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:34.13,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It must've been tough for you... - OG}It must have been so hard on you...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:40.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Is this a drawing?! Where is he?! - OG}Is this a painting?\NWhere is your real body?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:47.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm manipulating Oden from a distance! - OG}{I'm remotely controlling him! - Polly}I am puppeteering Oden from afar!{Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:50.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's really exhausting though! - OG}{It certainly takes a lot of energy, though! - Polly}It's quite the exhausting task!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:54.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:58.20,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your blade did cut me! - OG}Your blade indeed found its mark!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:00.32,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm seriously wounded, too! - OG}I am gravely wounded, as well!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I think I'm gonna die during this battle! - OG}{I expect this will be my final battle! - Polly}I expect this will be my final act!{Polly+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But what keeps me going now... - OG}{But the one thing that\Nkeeps me pressing onward... - Polly}But the one thing that\Nkeeps me pressing forward...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:08.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{is my grudge toward the Kozuki Clan! - OG}is my grudge toward the Kozuki!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:12.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But before I die... - OG}{And so, before I can allow myself to pass... - Polly}Therefore, before I pass away...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.04,0:21:15.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna stab at the heart of the Kozuki Clan! - OG}I will pierce through the heart\Nof the Kozuki Clan!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:17.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{As Kurozumi Kanjuro! - OG}As none other than Kurozumi Kanjuro!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:27.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Momonosuke-sama's in danger! - OG}Lord Momonosuke is in danger!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:31.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I think I heard this voice\Nfrom somewhere earlier... - OG}Oh, I seem to remember hearing\Na voice from somewhere earlier...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:34.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{saying Momonosuke-sama}{is with a kunoichi... - OG}{that said that Lord Momonosuke\Nis with a kunoichi... - Polly}saying that Lord Momonosuke\Nis with a {\i1}kunoichi{\i0}...{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:36.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,That must be Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Then we can get a connection! - OG}{That means we can send a message! - Polly}Which means we can contact him!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.24,0:21:43.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's not cool to chase a man who is dying. - OG}It's rather uncouth\Nto chase down a dying man.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.29,0:21:52.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{The Red Scabbards members will meet\Ntheir end here, unable to do anything! - OG}The Red Scabbards samurai will meet\Ntheir demise here, having achieved nothing!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:57.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Along with me... - OG}Myself included...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.84,0:22:05.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Let's go out with a sensational bang! - OG}{Let's go out with a flash, shall we? - Polly}Let's go out with a bang, shall we?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.31,0:22:12.81,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.98,0:22:18.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're friends, right? - OG}You are my friends, are you not?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:38.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ashura!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:42.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Get away from here, guys! - OG}{Everyone, get away from this place! - Polly}Get out of here, you guys!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.55,0:22:48.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Go stop Kanjuro! - OG}Go and stop Kanjuro!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.26,0:22:50.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:52.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:55.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Save Momonosuke-sama for me! - OG}{You must save Lord Momonosuke for me! - Polly}Save Lord Momonosuke for me!{OG+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:57.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, Ashura! - OG}{Thank you, Ashura! - Polly}We are in your debt, Ashura!{Z+Goldy}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:22:59.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:01.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How could you get in my way?! - OG}{How dare you upstage me?! - Gordy+Z}How dare you get in my way?!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:05.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Damn you! Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:13.66,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Don't sully Kozuki Oden anymore! - OG}{Don't you dare defile\NKozuki Oden any longer! - Polly}You will never defile the memory\Nof Kozuki Oden ever again!{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.08,0:23:54.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Kanjuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:02.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Next is finally my turn in a leading role! - OG}{It's finally my turn to have the starring role! - Polly}{It's finally time for me to take center stage! - Polly}{It's finally time for me, the main\Ncharacter, to take center stage! - Polly}It's finally time for me, the star of\Nthe show, to take center stage!{Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.71,0:24:04.84,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I pretended to be a Kozuki... - OG}First, I become a Kozuki...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.84,0:24:07.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and I'll eliminate the Kozuki, - OG}then, I eliminate the Kozuki...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.43,0:24:08.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{and die! - OG}{then, I die! - Polly}{finally, I die! - Z}and finally, I die!{Z+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:13.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's the best way to bring the curtain down! - OG}{This will be my greatest final act! - Polly}This will be my grand finale!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:17.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{My life is a beautiful show! - OG}{What a beautiful and glorious life it has been! - Polly}My life is one big, beautiful play!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.45,0:24:36.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.45,0:24:38.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You bastard! Do you wanna fight again?! - OG}{You bastard! You wanna fight again?! - Polly}You bastard! Back for round two?!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.50,0:24:41.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What a pain in the ass...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.75,0:24:44.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They tried to defend their kings... - OG}These weaklings tried to stand in my way...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.88,0:24:48.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{These small fries stood in my way... - OG}all to protect their precious kings!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.93,0:24:53.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Cat! Raizo! Just move on, everyone! - OG}Cat! Raizo! All of you, go on ahead!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.35,0:24:58.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Everyone, save Momonosuke-sama for me! - OG}Everyone, save Lord Momonosuke for me!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.23,0:25:01.35,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kin{-san}.{OG}{We must go, Kin. - Polly}{We need to go, Kin. - Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.35,0:25:02.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.69,0:25:06.90,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Be sure to catch up to us, Inuarashi!\NWe'll be waiting for you! - OG}{Be sure to catch up to us, Inuarashi!\NWe shall wait for you! - Z}Be sure to catch up to us, Inuarashi!\NWe shall await your arrival!{Z+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.62,0:25:17.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Are you gonna handle me\Nall by yourself, Ruler of the Day? - OG}Do you intend to fight me all on\Nyour own, Ruler of the Day?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.50,0:25:19.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We're both injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.75,0:25:21.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{So we're a good match! - OG}Seems like a fair fight.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.00,0:25:26.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I stayed behind not because\NI wanted to pay off an old grudge... - OG}{I stayed behind not because\NI wanted to settle an old grudge... - Polly}I didn't stay behind to settle an old grudge.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.26,0:25:33.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I didn't want anyone\Nto get hurt by letting you go free! Jack! - OG}{I simply cannot allow anyone else to come\Nto harm by letting you run free, Jack! - Polly}If I let you run free, more people will\Nget hurt! And I can't allow that, Jack!{WF+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.35,0:25:36.77,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You can't see the moon from here! - OG}There's no view of the moon from here!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.77,0:25:38.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,There's no poison gas, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.06,0:25:46.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We both have to prepare for the worst. - OG}{I suppose we'll both have to make do. - Polly}{Then I suppose we'll both have to make do. - Polly}{Then let's find out who fate favors today. - Z}Well, then... Let's find out\Nwho fate favors today.{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.25,0:26:04.71,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We must put it out quickly! - OG}{Hurry up and put it out already! - Polly}Hurry up and put it out!{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.71,0:26:09.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We need water! Bring more! - OG}Water! We need more water!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.60,0:26:23.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You are... - OG}It's you...!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.69,0:26:27.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna teach you idiots a lesson... - OG}It's time to teach you fools a lesson.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.57,0:26:29.82,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I thought you were dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.82,0:26:32.07,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How come you're alive?! - OG}{How can you be alive?! - Polly}How did you survive?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.54,0:26:46.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How could you betray me, Kaido?! - OG}How could Kaido betray me like that?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.75,0:26:51.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Orochi-sama certainly... - OG}There is no doubt about it, Lord Orochi...{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.05,0:26:55.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{got beheaded by Kaido once... - OG}You were certainly beheaded\Nby Kaido... once, that is.{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.72,0:26:56.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{But... - OG}However...{Polly - even this doesn't really make any sense or flow at all. Help...}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.80,0:26:59.93,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna burn it all up! - OG}I'm gonna burn it all down!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.39,0:27:04.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna turn Onigashima\Ninto a ball of flames! - OG}{Onigashima will be a ball of flame\Nby the time I'm through with it! - Goldy+Polly}Onigashima will be a raging inferno\Nby the time I'm through with it!{Goldy+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.89,0:27:07.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{There's no escape in the air, - OG}{There's no escaping up here in the air, - Polly}There's nowhere to run in the air.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.52,0:27:09.69,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{so die! - OG}{so just die already! - Polly}All you can do is die!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.07,0:27:16.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm gonna kill them all! - OG}I'll kill every last one of them!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.16,0:27:18.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'll make them regret crossing me! - OG}They'll rue the day they crossed me!{WF+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.38,0:27:31.59,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Momonosuke{-kun}!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.59,0:27:33.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can you change back to yourself? - OG}Can you go back to normal?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.80,0:27:35.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You're sticking out like that. - OG}You stick out like a sore thumb.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.68,0:27:37.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah... - OG}S-Sure...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.85,0:27:47.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Stay still this time, Momonosuke-kun! - OG}Stay put this time, Momonosuke!{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.65,0:27:48.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I am sorry! - OG}My apologies...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.82,0:27:55.36,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It may not look it, but I have gained\Nbetter control over it... - OG}It may not look it, but I have\Nlearned to control it better...{LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.74,0:27:59.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,When I first met Luffy and the others,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.37,0:28:03.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I would turn into a dragon\Nevery time I got surprised and felt sad. - OG}I would turn into a dragon\Nevery time I got surprised or felt sad.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.75,0:28:05.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I'm astonished. - OG}{That's pretty wild. - Polly}{That's a shock. - Polly}Astonishing...{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.00,0:28:07.33,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I wonder if it's\Nsimilar to my father's power... - OG}I wonder if it's like my father's power...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.33,0:28:12.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,If I could turn into a monster like he does,\NI would be of some help to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.46,0:28:16.05,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy is still fighting Kaido, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.05,0:28:17.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.68,0:28:20.64,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,I wanna take down Kaido too! As Oden!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.64,0:28:24.06,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Luffy is getting much weaker... - OG}Luffy is growing much weaker...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.06,0:28:26.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,but somehow, he is in good spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.31,0:28:27.56,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{That's good... - OG}Thank goodness...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.81,0:28:29.52,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.90,0:28:33.94,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How can you tell, Momonosuke-sama?! - OG}How can you tell, Lord Momonosuke?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.99,0:28:43.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How can we defeat them? - OG}How do we beat these guys?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.75,0:28:49.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I don't think our attacks are working. - OG}{Doesn't seem like anything is working. - Polly}They shrug off every attack\Nwe throw at them...!{WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.63,0:28:53.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{They sure are Emperors... Their skin is tough. - OG}That's a couple of Emperors for you...\NThey've got some thick skin.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.96,0:28:57.88,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Can't they at least pretend\Nthat it's working a little bit?! - OG}Can't they at least pretend it's making a dent?!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.84,0:29:01.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{It's working! - OG}It {\i1}is{\i0} working!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.55,0:29:05.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{After all this striking,\Nthere's no way it wouldn't work! - OG}{After a beating like that,\Nthere's no way they don't feel a thing! - Polly}After a beating like that,\Nthere's no way they're not hurting!{Polly+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.85,0:29:07.43,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,They're humans just like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.98,0:29:10.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.19,0:29:19.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You did that earlier and it didn't work!\NThink before you attack! - OG}{You already tried that earlier!\NThink before you attack! - Polly}You already tried that earlier!\NThink before you dive in!{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.28,0:29:22.12,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{How can you say they're humans just like us - OG}How can you call them human...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.12,0:29:24.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{even when the distinction is so clear? - OG}when the gap between us is so big?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.20,0:29:28.91,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{You guys think you can't beat them,\Nand yet here you are? - OG}Look, if you don't think we can win,\Nthen why are you here?{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.91,0:29:31.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We're trying to figure out how to win! - OG}We're trying to figure out {\i1}how{\i0} to win!{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.21,0:29:34.67,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{We should pull one of them away from here. - OG}{We should try luring them apart. - Polly}We should lure one of them away from here.{Z+Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.21,0:29:36.63,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I agree. - OG}Good idea.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.63,0:29:40.22,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{When those two are side by side,\Nthis place looks like... - OG}With the two of them side by side like this...{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.55,0:29:46.76,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{...nothing but hell... - OG}it looks like we're in hell.{Polly}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.96,0:30:13.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've been to hell many times... - OG}{That's fine... I've been to hell\Nand back plenty of times. - Polly}Hell, huh?{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.79,0:30:16.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've been to hell many times... - OG}{That's fine... I've been to hell\Nand back plenty of times. - Polly}I've been there plenty of times.{Polly+Z}
Comment: 0,0:30:11.96,0:30:16.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{I've been to hell many times... - OG}{That's fine... I've been to hell\Nand back plenty of times. - Polly}Hell, huh? I've been there plenty of times.{Polly+Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.34,0:30:21.09,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{Your eyes always look vigorous! - OG}{You always have that look in your eyes... - Polly}That light in your eyes never goes out...{Polly+LP}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.97,0:30:26.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.89,0:30:28.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,We have the upper hand!
